          - Shuttle suffered FTL drop-out and crash; Jensen and Reed died; Kira Voss survived with head bleeding, bruised ribs, and wounded right leg; primary ship AI SAM is offline and emergency neural-link AI 'Buddy' is active.
          - Shuttle hull breached; planet has breathable atmosphere and freshwater ~800 m southwest; shuttle comms, propulsion, and distress beacon damaged; emergency life-support reserves and limited survival supplies remain (sealed water, ~one week rations, basic med supplies, tools, tarp).
