          - Kira asked Holloway for higher-level assistance; Holloway identified Elder Heartwood (an ancient, slow-acting authority that handles exceptional cases) and filed a formal exception query on Kira's behalf.
          - The query to Elder Heartwood was transmitted with an estimated response time of ~8–12 weeks (two to three months); Holloway will continue daily wellness checks and support while awaiting guidance.
